{"word":"G426 - ἀνετάζω - anetázō - an-et-ad'-zo - Examined","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνετάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anetázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-et-ad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Examined</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விசாரி"},{"paragraph":"to investigate, examine; to examine judicially"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9;</b> <b>etazo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>test</i>); to <i>investigate</i> (judicially): - (should have) examine (-d).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}